[Amit Varma]: take comfort and stimulation from virtual spaces traveling at the speed of light.

00:03:08.880 --> 00:03:12.240
[Amit Varma]: Too much of this, and we can get unmoored from our physical location,

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:15.280
[Amit Varma]: a creature of every place and no place at the same time.

00:03:15.280 --> 00:03:18.800
[Amit Varma]: But if we don't go overboard, this is so empowering.

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:23.120
[Amit Varma]: This new way of living and learning and loving has transformed at least me,

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:24.800
[Amit Varma]: and it's all because of technology.

00:03:24.800 --> 00:03:30.240
[Amit Varma]: The sponsor of this episode, Intel, is at the heart of much of this digital transformation.

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:34.640
[Amit Varma]: Intel's technology empowers users at the edges of this brave new world.

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:37.440
[Amit Varma]: It safeguards their data, protects their privacy,

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:41.360
[Amit Varma]: while also enabling them to harness the full power of the internet.

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:45.200
[Amit Varma]: Whether you're an entrepreneur or an artist or a doctor or an engineer,

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:47.840
[Amit Varma]: you are not who you would have been 20 years ago.

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:49.760
[Amit Varma]: Intel made all this possible.

